title: 097 - Sweet Mayo, Mississippi Mark, and Return of the Freightbacks
description:
This week, Dustin hates Disney. Tim has an epiphany about a new life change. The crew recounts odd show day memories. What’s your fav fried chicken? A fight breaks out after the Sunday night show. Aaaaaand the crew gets a late night craving for PB&Js.
